OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatches of low cloud will
OL,6,Flinger this morning, but this will
OL,7,Fgradually break up towards the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Hot sunny spells will
OL,9,Fdevelop with light winds. Low cloud
OL,10,Fmay persist around some coastlines of
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry, bright and warm
OL,14,Fevening. Patchy low cloud may spread
OL,15,Fback in overnight giving some areas of
OL,16,Fmist. Dry and warm overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
