OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAny low cloud will gradually
OL,6,Flift and break to bring another hot
OL,7,Fand sunny day with light winds.
OL,8,FPerhaps some mist around Cornish
OL,9,Fcoasts at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,12,Fand hot over the next few days with
OL,13,Fsome strong sunshine and light winds.
OL,14,FA little less hot towards the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
